Infinity Music Player

Infinity Music Player is lightweight music player and visualizer with modern designed user interface. It allows you to browse your music by albums,artists and more. Use playlists to make and hear your favorite songs collectizons. The player is able to continuously play shuffled tracks or just repeat single song. But the best thing is the audio visualization. See what you listen to.

Privacy Policy

This app doesn't have the Internet accsess permission, so it doesn't collect nor send any user data to the developer.

The Microphone (RECORD_AUDIO) permission is needed in order to caputre the outgoing audio and visualize it. The audio data is not stored nor send anywhere from your device.
